 69 元，套裝 138 元起" width="1080" height="1093" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="02f7" style="text-align: left;">該機搭載<strong>第三代驍龍 8 處理器</strong>，採用智能思維引擎&nbsp;One Mind 10.5，實現「續航更久、性能更強、功耗更低、運行更快」；<strong>內置&nbsp;4800mAh 電池</strong>，在 0—100% 極限續航模型測試下可達 8.2 小時；擁有<strong>&nbsp;1.74mm 窄邊框</strong>，做到了物理四等邊。</p><p data-vmark="6797" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/9d55b1ad-8aad-4404-be43-3f5a7d9df154.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" title="魅族 21 PANDAER 手機殼膜套裝上架：官方鋼化膜 69 元，套裝 138 元起" width="1080" height="1093" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="93f1" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/ae2a8ab7-4bc1-40ec-8090-553d6e1e13a3.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" title="魅族 21 PANDAER 手機殼膜套裝上架：官方鋼化膜 69 元，套裝 138 元起" width="1080" height="1093" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="4b64" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/46aefa85-3012-4b61-bdd3-4c058804ab96.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" title="魅族 21 PANDAER 手機殼膜套裝上架：官方鋼化膜 69 元，套裝 138 元起" width="1080" height="1093" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/ZsO5KHP" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://u.jd.com/ZuOHSlo" data-iosurl="https://u.jd.com/ZbOorpj" data-androidurl="https://u.jd.com/ZbadSe7" data-hosurl="https://u.jd.com/Z8OkYJZ" data-uwpurl="https://u.jd.com/ZuOk8zG" data-wxmpurl="ithome://openmp?appid=wx91d27dbf599dff74&amp;path=%2fpages%2funion%2fproxy%2fproxy%3fspreadUrl%3dhttps%253a%252f%252fu.jd.com%252fZsaMu5d%26EA_PTAG%3d17078.27.380" data-itwxurl="https://u.jd.com/ZzO4s9M" data-lpwxurl="https://u.jd.com/ZzOkjWw" data-jdid="100075587443"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/231199/38/4345/34757/656094efF233bf241/a30a697485f20b72.jpg" title="魅族 21 PAND